Package: multicore
Version: 0.1-0
Title: Parallel processing on machines with multiple cores or CPUs
Author: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Maintainer: Simon Urbanek <Simon.Urbanek@r-project.org>
Depends: R (>= 2.0.0)
Description: This package prodives a way of running parallel computations in R on machines with multiple cores or CPUs. Jobs can share the entire initial workspace and provides methods for results collection.
License: GPL version 2
SystemRequirements: POSIX-compliant OS (essentially anything but Windows)
URL: http://www.rforge.net/multicore/
